Folder Structure:-

// config - for database connection
// controller - for all the logic and redirec
// helper - some function which helps in code.
// routes- all the routes related this project 
// services- this folder contains database related query 
// test - this folder contains test case of api
// utils- some constant and user type i mentioned in this folder.

// for running this application we type the command 
// nodemon app.js

// for running test case we type command 
// npm run test test/task/task.js

